label.description: Will the service provider be collecting or storing Universities Canada’s data? For how long? What will they do with the data upon completion of the contract? Where does the company store their data?
Where does the company store their data?
What assurances can the vendor provide that they maintain confidentiality and a secure environment? Do they have a privacy policy, audited reports and/or security standards we can review?

Does the contract state that Universities Canada may carry out verifications to their security obligations?In the event of a security breach, what is the notification process by the vendor? How soon will we be notified? Who at the company is responsible for notifying Universities Canada?
